The,LivePerson,platform,enables,businesses,to,identify,and,engage,customers,using,the,right,communication,channel,at,the,right,time,This,hosted,solution,delivers,tools,that,support,and,manage,online,customer,interactions,chat,email,voice,and,knowledgebase,from,a,single,agent,application,The,service,provides,users,an,opportunity,to,immediately,chat,with,a,representative,via,an,instant,messaging,system,embedded,in,their,site,With,the,API,users,can,create,update,and,retrieve,resources,Responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON,With,the,LivePerson,Agent,API,developers,can,create,agent,chat,applications,from,any,desktop,mobile,device,or,server,based,software,application,These,applications,enable,agents,real,or,virtual,to,log,into,their,LivePerson,account,take,chats,from,visitors,and,to,transfer,chats,to,other,agents,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON